\v 26 \w God|strong="H8064"\w* said, “Let \w us|strong="H5921"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* human \w beings|strong="H1823"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* \w image|strong="H6754"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H8064"\w* \w like|strong="H1823"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*.\f + \fr 1:26 \ft This aspect of being “like” God conveys the idea of being “patterned” after God. The word is also translated “similitude,” “figure” or “form.” The most essential aspect of this resemblance is surely that of character.\f* \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H8064"\w* \w have|strong="H3605"\w* \w authority|strong="H5921"\w* \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w fish|strong="H1710"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w air|strong="H8064"\w*, \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* livestock, \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w whole|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* creature \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w moves|strong="H7430"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w*.”  
\v 27 So God \w created|strong="H1254"\w* human beings \w in|strong="H2145"\w* his own \w image|strong="H6754"\w*. \w He|strong="H5347"\w* \w created|strong="H1254"\w* \w them|strong="H1254"\w* \w in|strong="H2145"\w* \w the|strong="H1254"\w* \w image|strong="H6754"\w* \w of|strong="H6754"\w* God. \w He|strong="H5347"\w* \w created|strong="H1254"\w* \w them|strong="H1254"\w* \w male|strong="H2145"\w* \w and|strong="H2145"\w* \w female|strong="H5347"\w*.\f + \fr 1:27 \ft The repetition of “created” in this verse is surely significant, which is why this is placed first in each sentence.\f*  
\v 28 \w God|strong="H8064"\w* \w blessed|strong="H1288"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* told \w them|strong="H5921"\w*, “Reproduce, \w increase|strong="H7235"\w*, \w and|strong="H8064"\w* spread \w throughout|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* control \w it|strong="H5921"\w*; \w exercise|strong="H7287"\w* \w authority|strong="H5921"\w* \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w fish|strong="H1710"\w* \w of|strong="H4390"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w of|strong="H4390"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w air|strong="H8064"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w creature|strong="H2416"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w moves|strong="H7430"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*.”   
\p
\v 29 \w God|strong="H5414"\w* said, “\w Look|strong="H2009"\w*, \w I|strong="H5414"\w*'m \w giving|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w as|strong="H1961"\w* \w your|strong="H3605"\w* food \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w seed-bearing|strong="H2233"\w* \w plant|strong="H6212"\w* \w anywhere|strong="H3605"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* earth, \w and|strong="H6086"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w tree|strong="H6086"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w produces|strong="H5414"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w seeds|strong="H2233"\w*.  
\v 30 \w I|strong="H5921"\w*'m giving \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w green|strong="H3418"\w* \w plants|strong="H6212"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w land|strong="H8064"\w* \w animals|strong="H2416"\w*, \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w*, \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w creature|strong="H5315"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w moves|strong="H7430"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*—\w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w living|strong="H2416"\w* \w thing|strong="H2416"\w*.” \w And|strong="H8064"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w*'s \w what|strong="H5921"\w* \w happened|strong="H1961"\w*.   
\p
\v 31 God \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w he|strong="H3117"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w created|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w yes|strong="H2009"\w*, \w it|strong="H6213"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w good|strong="H2896"\w*. \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w there|strong="H2009"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w evening|strong="H6153"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w morning|strong="H1242"\w*, \w making|strong="H6213"\w* \w day|strong="H3117"\w* six.   
\b  
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w creation|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H6635"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w heavens|strong="H8064"\w*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*, \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H6635"\w* \w them|strong="H3615"\w*\f + \fr 2:1 \ft “Everything in them”: literally, “all the array of them.” The word used for “array” is usually a military term designating the formation of an army of soldiers.\f* \w was|strong="H6635"\w* \w complete|strong="H3615"\w*.  
