\v 1 \w Sarai|strong="H8297"\w*, Abram's wife, hadn't \w been|strong="H3808"\w* able \w to|strong="H3205"\w* \w have|strong="H3808"\w* \w any|strong="H3808"\w* \w children|strong="H3205"\w* \w for|strong="H8034"\w* \w him|strong="H3205"\w*. However, \w she|strong="H3808"\w* owned \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w female|strong="H8198"\w* \w Egyptian|strong="H4713"\w* \w slave|strong="H8198"\w* \w named|strong="H8034"\w* \w Hagar|strong="H1904"\w*,  
